{"type":null,"faqId":9446,"title":"荣耀3X（G750-T00）HiSuite使用方法","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机支持并自带</span><span><span>Hisuite</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">下载器。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机接入</span><span><span>USB</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连接线后，在手机下拉通知栏中选择“设备文件管理（</span><span><span>MTP</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）”或者“作为</span><span><span>USB</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">存储设备连接”或者“仅充电”的模式选择，进入</span><span><span>USB</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">计算机连接菜单</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29935\" /></span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">选择“</span><b><span><span>PC</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">助手（</span><span><span>HiSuite</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29936\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">稍微等待，在</span><span><span>PC</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">侧打开我的电脑，双击内置光盘</span><span><span>HiSuite</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，执行光盘中的</span><span><span>HiSuiteDownLoader.exe</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">安装即可使用。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29937\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">可以通过</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-fami